nodes.text: Oolamalloola was a criminal who operated during the Imperial Era. The assassin droid and bounty hunter IG-88 killed Oolamalloola, but chose not to take the bounty on the criminal immediately. When a group of criminals led by Kaluub Akjee captured IG-88, they attempted to claim several bounties that he had stored in his head, including the bounty on Oolamalloola.
